# Toronto Rising — author session facts

Agents must not speculate about facts only the author or live Tabletop Simulator session can confirm.

Ask direct confirmation questions instead of guessing about:

- whether the author used Save & Play after a repo change
- whether a repro came from manual clicks, a harness, or a scripted helper
- which GUID/object is live in the saved game
- whether debug buttons, test panels, or `RunTest` were re-armed
- what the author saw in-game when logs/code do not prove it

State what code, logs, saved files, or Linear/tasklist records prove. For anything outside those sources, ask.

Use [`.dev/SOLVING ISSUES & DEBUGGING.md`](../../.dev/SOLVING%20ISSUES%20%26%20DEBUGGING.md) for the full debugging checklist.
